and I hate it.

980
01:22:47,879 --> 01:22:50,313
- Aw.
- And I don't want to be.

981
01:22:50,506 --> 01:22:54,897
<i>I really, really, really don't. </i>

982
01:22:58,887 --> 01:23:02,482
Sweetheart, it's not your fault.

983
01:23:02,724 --> 01:23:05,192
There's so many things
you don't know about me.

984
01:23:05,392 --> 01:23:07,383
No, not yet.

985
01:23:12,315 --> 01:23:15,546
I want to be your friend,

986
01:23:15,776 --> 01:23:18,085
because...

987
01:23:18,278 --> 01:23:21,793
Because... we still have time.

988
01:23:24,699 --> 01:23:28,897
- I'd be honoured to be your friend.
- No, not honoured.

989
01:23:29,161 --> 01:23:34,952
